{"word":"Blood","slug":"blood","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Blood</b> Is the life<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=9&verse=4'>Gen 9:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=17&verse=11'>Lev 17:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=17&verse=14'>Lev 17:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=19&verse=16'>Lev 19:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=12&verse=23'>Deu 12:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=4'>Mat 27:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=27&verse=24'>Mat 27:24</a><br/> Forbidden to be used as food<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=9&verse=4'>Gen 9:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=3&verse=17'>Lev 3:17</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=7&verse=27'>Lev 7:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=17&verse=14'>Lev 17:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=19&verse=26'>Lev 19:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=12&verse=16'>Deu 12:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=12&verse=23'>Deu 12:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=15&verse=23'>Deu 15:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=33&verse=25'>Eze 33:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=20'>Act 15:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=15&verse=29'>Act 15:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=21&verse=25'>Act 21:25</a><br/> Plague of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7&verse=25'>Exo 7:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=78&verse=44'>Psa 78:44</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=105&verse=29'>Psa 105:29</a><br/> Sacrificial<br/> - Without shedding of, no remission<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=9&verse=22'>Heb 9:22</a> <br/> - Sprinkled on altar and people<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=24&verse=8'>Exo 24:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=43&verse=18'>Eze 43:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=43&verse=20'>Eze 43:20</a> <br/> - Sprinkled on door posts<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=12&verse=23'>Exo 12:23</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=58&chapter=11&verse=28'>Heb 11:28</a> <br/> - Of sin offering<br/> b Sprinkled seven times before the vail<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=4&verse=6'>Lev 4:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=4&verse=17'>Lev 4:17</a><br/> b Sprinkled on horns of the altar of sweet incense, and at the bottom of the altar of burnt offering<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=30&verse=10'>Exo 30:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=4&verse=7'>Lev 4:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=4&verse=18'>Lev 4:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=4&verse=25'>Lev 4:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=4&verse=30'>Lev 4:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=5&verse=9'>Lev 5:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=9&verse=9'>Lev 9:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=9&verse=12'>Lev 9:12</a><br/> b of bullock of sin offering, put on the horns of the altar<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=29&verse=12'>Exo 29:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=3&chapter=8&verse=15'>Lev 8:15</a><br/> b Poured at the bottom of the altar<br/> <a href='https://ww